Ethula inkulumo yakhe mayelana nesimo sesifundazwe enkundleni yezemidlalo, eRoyal Showgrounds eMgungundlovu ngoLwesithathu, uMchunu uthe * -46%, wabantu baKwaZulu-Natal bahlala emakhaya. “Kubalulekile ukuba sikuqonde ukuthi * -46% wabantu baKwaZulu-Natal bahlala emakhaya. Siyakuqaphela futhi ukuthi abantu abaningi bayasuka emakhaya baye emadolobheni ngoba belandela izidingo,” kusho uMchunu. Uthe ukuhamba kwabantu abasha emakhaya beyofuna umsebenzi emadolobheni kuhlukanisa imindeni kuphazamise nesimo senhlalo emphakathini abasuka kuyo. Ukugcwala kwezindawo zasemadolobheni kubanga izinkinga. Uthe into abayifisayo wukushintsha imizi yasemakhaya ibe sezingeni laleyo esemadolobheni. “Kumele sisebenze kanzima ukuze abantu baqonde ngokuzimela kwezindawo zasemakhaya nezasemadolobheni.” Uthe ikhona inqubekela phambili esikhona emkhankasweni wabo wokuthuthukisa izindawo zasemakhaya. “Ngalesi sikhathi sale khabhinethi siqede uhlelo Inkululeko Development Programme eNdumo. Uhlelo luhlose ukuthi uhulumeni angenelele ekwenzeni ngcono impilo yabantu bakule ndawo. ENdumo sakhe isikole esisezingeni lomhlaba, siyaziqhenya ukubika ukuthi iMandla Mthethwa Comprehensive School ivulwe ngokusemthethweni ngo-2018,” kusho uMchunu. Uthe zonke lezi zidingo abazifakayo zidinga ingqalasizinda. Balethe nohlelo lokuletha amanzi, iShemula Water Scheme esiza abantu baseNdumo nasezindaweni ezingomakhelwane ukuze bathole amanzi ahlanzekile. “Khona futhi eNdumo sakhe ibhuloho sathuthukisa nomgwaqo uP435. Singakusho singananazi ukuthi Indumo ngeke iphinde ifane nakudala,” kusho uMchumu. Uthe ilinganiselwa ku-5 500 imizi asebeyakhile eNdumo. Ingaphezu kuka-1.2 billion imali evela eminyangweni eyehlukene esetshenzisiwe ukuthuthukisa indawo yaseNdumo. 